jelson notes:

Site uses Jekyll.

* Installation - don't try to apt-get install, it just gets confused and sad
  because 'gem' installations conflict with the system installations

  https://jekyllrb.com/docs/installation/ubuntu/

  gem install jekyll bundler
  bundle install

* Running

  Make sure 'which jekyll' returns ~/.gems/bin, not /usr/bin

  Debug server:
     bundle exec jekyll serve --config _config.yml,_config_dev.yml
     point browser to localhost:4000
  
  